<topic id="plugin-testing">
  <title>Testing DITA-OT Plugins</title>
  <shortdesc>Test existing plugins from the DITA-OT registry with different versions.</shortdesc>
  <body>
    <p>The <filepath>examples/plugin-test</filepath> project demonstrates how to test DITA-OT plugins from the official registry.</p>

    <section>
      <title>Quick Start</title>
      <codeblock>cd examples/plugin-test

# Test with defaults (DITA-OT 4.2.3, org.lwdita plugin)
./gradlew test

# Test with specific DITA-OT version
./gradlew -PditaOtVersion=4.1.0 test

# Test different plugin and transtype
./gradlew -PpluginId=org.dita.normalize -Ptranstype=normalize test</codeblock>
    </section>

